IN RE Resignation of MEEHAN 2019-0286 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 13, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

DISCIPLINARY CASE

Sua sponte, Michael Patrick Meehan, Attorney Registration No. 0059515, last known business address in Cleveland, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to surrender his certificate of admission and failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before May 6, 2019.
